reminder_newpost:
**Welcome to thirdweb support!** 

We understand that you may be experiencing some difficulties, but don't worry, we're here to help. While waiting for a response from our team or community members, we recommend exploring our AI assistant to see if it can help you with your issue. Simply head to our [Support](https://support.thirdweb.com) site, click the icon on the bottom right, and ask your question to get an answer right away. 

Additionally, to create an effective support post, please visit our <#1074862134284005396> channel to learn more. If you need human assistance, please wait for our team or community members to respond. Thank you for building with us!
reminder_mention: Hey! If you need help, please read the information in <#1074862134284005396> and post your questions or issues in the <#1029543258822553680> channel. Our team and community members are always ready to help you out. Thank you for building with us!

reminder_close: Hello! This post was closed due to inactivity, missing information, irrelevant, duplicate or otherwise. If you believe this was a mistake or you wish to re-open, please let us know here and we're happy to do so! For new questions, please create a new post in <#1029543258822553680>. Thank you!
reminder_resolve: This post has been marked as resolved, check the pinned message here to see the solution. If you have another question, kindly create a new post in <#1029543258822553680>. Happy building!
